      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAYDEN (2) was well back throughout but attacked the line strongly to place, 2.5 lengths from the winner (24.53) at this track in Grade 5. Rates highly and will give a great sight. TORNADO JACK (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (25.15) in a Grade 5 at this track. Should be thereabouts. SANDY CHEEK (7) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4 lengths (24.63) at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. Cannot be taken lightly. TRAJECTORY (8) can sneak into the finish.",
